title: Met gala 3 fashion
detail: High fashion Twitter wasnt the only online space where the Met Gala was being celebrated. The Met also started a viral challenge called the #MetGalaChallenge, where users recreated their favorite memorable looks from galas past, which merited some truly spectacular results, including skating star Adam Rippon dressing up as Rihanna in her iconic yellow Guo Pei cape dress from the 2015 Met Gala.
